  "title": "Crane Operator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Operate grabbing Rig, trench cutter and service crane</li>\n  <li>Perform routine and basic daily check before and after operating the assigned crane</li>\n  <li>Inspect crane for defective parts and notify supervisor of defects or malfunction</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with team members on-site to complete assigned tasks efficiently</li>\n  <li>Ensure strict compliance with safety rules and regulations</li>\n  <li>Any other ad-hoc assigned as deemed necessary for the role</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 5 years’ experience operating cranes</li>\n  <li>BCA Certificate of Successful Completion – Crawler Crane Operations</li>\n  <li>Must possess valid Crawler Crane License</li>\n  <li>Able to execute work instructions independently</li>\n</ul>",
